				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Any one think the Epic 1.5 is kinda weak?<a name="66164"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 8 04 7:08 PM</span></td>
