				<td colspan="2"><span>I may be off my rocker here, but i have to disagree about Epic 1.5 being weak.
<br />

<br />
For a NON-TIME flagged bard, it has some major advantages,'
<br />

<br />
1) Solid Ratio 21/21 (24/22 after patch) is better than any other pre time bard wep, and on par with the king of EP weps Rune Stamped Blade.
<br />

<br />
2) 2.2 All instruments.  I am unaware of any 2.2 worn effects pre Time, pre GoD.  This weapon in effect completely replaces the deficiencies of 1.0, which were the garbage ratio, and the fact that we needed 5 pieces of gear to replace our previous epic.  These being Hydra Mask (sing 2.0), EP Boots (drum 1.8), EP arms (String 1.8), EP BP (Time Drop, Brass 2.2 iirc), and Cornaiv Shoulders (Wind mod).  With IM4, that makes this a 3.0 worn mod.
<br />

<br />
3) 40% increase to song effectiveness is a huge advantage.  My standard song line up is mostly DS, Haste and regen at this point and increasing DS/ Regen is always a good thing, though its like everything else we do, not much short term, huge difference big picture.
<br />

<br />
4) Tell me a better bard weapon that isn't Time +.
<br />

<br />
Yes, I realize, that not everyone is still below Time level, but 90% of the bards are.  Ask yourself this also, at what level and flagging level were you finally able to bank 1.0? I still carry it in offhand, and I expect to carry 1.5 in offhand once I'm able to bank 1.0 (if it doesn't go in primary).
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Rappa
